The most elevated expression 💫
•

❓ WHY ❓
•
We all have our own reasons for doing hard things - my reason is surfing! 🏄🏽‍♂️ 
•
Whenever I find myself in a challenging moment, I silently remind myself that I’m doing it to be a little better the next time I paddle out. 🚴🏼‍♂️🚣🏽‍♂️🧘🏻‍♂️
•
That touch of perspective helps me focus, and keeps me motivated to power through. 💪🏽💥🤙🏽
•
What’s Your WHY??
•
#Why #Reason #Training #Focus #Motivation #Surf #CarpeDM

Let’s move for the next generation.  
 
Join One Love and Denis Morton at Move for Love Seattle, One Love’s annual 5K walk/run, and let’s raise awareness so the next generation knows the difference between healthy and unhealthy relationships.  
 
When you sign up for the 5K walk/run, you will have access to our finish line festival, which includes an appearance by Seahawk dancers, Blitz, the Seahawks mascot, Harry the Husky mascot and a performance by Blue Thunder, the Seattle Seahawk’s drumline, you won’t want to miss. Register now at www.moveforlove.org/seattle. #MoveforLove #SeattleSeahawks

🐦‍⬛ RAVENS SEASON 🐦‍⬛
•
I’ve been a @ravens fan since ‘96, the first year they played. Their affinity for players from my home state of Florida paired with their dynamic, aggressive style of play made me an instant fan, and the connection keeps growing. 🏈 
•
Huge thanks to the team for having me out for opening day, & congrats on a big first win! 🎆
•

🚨GAME CHANGER 🚨
•
It’s marathon season and this month @mattwilpers and I will be providing you with a “Game Changing” stretch for runners every Friday. 🏃🏼‍♀️🧘🏽🏃🏻‍♂️
•
These are high value stretches that you can include in your post-run stretch routine to help restore mobility and accelerate recovery so that you can keep training! 🏃🏻‍♀️🧘🏻‍♀️🔁
•
For more, please check out @onepeloton Yoga For Runners! Enjoy 🙏
